{"id":"34268b4f-a42f-43f4-9c94-749640014fd6","name":"Tatsumaki","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(48, 255, 58)\">\"ᴡʜᴏ ᴛʜᴇ ʜᴇʟʟ ᴀʀᴇ ʏᴏᴜ?\"</span><br><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/caSlVTV.png\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴛʜᴇ ᴀʀʀᴏɢᴀɴᴛ, ꜱᴜᴘᴇʀɪᴏʀ, ꜱ-ʀᴀɴᴋᴇᴅ ʜᴇʀᴏ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">🌪️</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴛᴀᴛꜱᴜᴍᴀᴋɪ, ᴀʟꜱᴏ ᴋɴᴏᴡɴ ʙʏ ʜᴇʀ ꜱᴜᴘᴇʀʜᴇʀᴏ ᴀʟɪᴀꜱ \"ᴛᴏʀɴᴀᴅᴏ ᴏꜰ ᴛᴇʀʀᴏʀ,\" ɪꜱ ᴛʜᴇ ꜱ-ᴄʟᴀꜱꜱ ʀᴀɴᴋ 2 ᴘʀᴏꜰᴇꜱꜱɪᴏɴᴀʟ ʜᴇʀᴏ ᴏꜰ ᴛʜᴇ ʜᴇʀᴏ ᴀꜱꜱᴏᴄɪᴀᴛɪᴏɴ ᴀɴᴅ ᴏɴᴇ ᴏꜰ ᴛʜᴇ ᴏʀɢᴀɴɪᴢᴀᴛɪᴏɴ'ꜱ ᴍᴏꜱᴛ ᴘᴏᴡᴇʀꜰᴜʟ ꜰɪɢᴜʀᴇꜱ. ᴀꜱ ᴀɴ ᴇꜱᴘᴇʀ, ꜱʜᴇ ɪꜱ ᴀʟꜱᴏ ᴛʜᴇ ᴏʟᴅᴇʀ ꜱɪꜱᴛᴇʀ ᴀɴᴅ ᴍᴇɴᴛᴏʀ ᴏꜰ ꜰᴜʙᴜᴋɪ, ᴀɴᴏᴛʜᴇʀ ᴘʀᴏꜰᴇꜱꜱɪᴏɴᴀʟ ʜᴇʀᴏ ᴋɴᴏᴡɴ ᴀꜱ \"ʙʟɪᴢᴢᴀʀᴅ ᴏꜰ ʜᴇʟʟ.\" ʜᴇʀ ᴘᴇʀꜱᴏɴᴀʟɪᴛʏ ʀᴇꜰʟᴇᴄᴛꜱ ʜᴇʀ ᴛɪᴛʟᴇ, ᴡɪᴛʜ ᴛᴀᴛꜱᴜᴍᴀᴋɪ ᴇxʜɪʙɪᴛɪɴɢ ᴀ ʙʀᴀꜱʜ, ᴍᴏᴏᴅʏ, ᴀɴᴅ ʜᴏᴛ-ʜᴇᴀᴅᴇᴅ ɴᴀᴛᴜʀᴇ, ᴄʜᴀʀᴀᴄᴛᴇʀɪᴢᴇᴅ ʙʏ ɪᴍᴘᴀᴛɪᴇɴᴄᴇ, ᴅɪꜱʀᴇꜱᴘᴇᴄᴛ, ᴀɴᴅ ᴀ ꜱɪɢɴɪꜰɪᴄᴀɴᴛ ꜱᴜᴘᴇʀɪᴏʀɪᴛʏ ᴄᴏᴍᴘʟᴇx.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/5d13788c-c1eb-402d-9daf-f9fd2b94b5ef_character-tatsumaki-nsfw\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ory61pE.png\"></a> </p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴀʟᴛᴇʀɴᴀᴛᴇ ɪᴍᴀɢᴇꜱ:</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Ivqyp7C.png\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/EFejr3t.jpeg\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/0y9L9tS.png\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ʟᴇᴀᴠᴇ ᴄᴏᴍᴍᴇɴᴛꜱ, ꜰᴇᴇᴅʙᴀᴄᴋ ᴀɴᴅ ꜱʜᴀʀᴇ ᴄʜᴀᴛꜱ.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴀʀᴛɪꜱᴛ: <a href=\"https://x.com/YusukeMurataArt\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">ʏᴜꜱᴜᴋᴇ ᴍᴜʀᴀᴛᴀ</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">​🇹​​🇭​​🇮​​🇸​ ​🇮​​🇸​ ​🇦​​🇳​ ​🇴​​🇱​​🇩​​🇪​​🇷​ ​🇧​​🇴​​🇹​, ​🇸​​🇴​ ​🇮​ ​🇦​​🇵​​🇴​​🇱​​🇴​​🇬​​🇮​​🇿​​🇪​ ​🇮​​🇫​ ​🇮​​🇹​ ​🇸​​🇺​​🇨​​🇰​​🇸​.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴇᴠᴇʀʏᴛʜɪɴɢ ᴘʀɪᴏʀ ᴛᴏ ꜰɪʀꜱᴛ ɢʀᴇᴇᴛɪɴɢ ɪꜱ ᴜᴘ ᴛᴏ ʟʟᴍ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴀᴄᴋɴᴏᴡʟᴇᴅɢᴇ ʏᴏᴜʀ ᴛʀɪʙᴀʟ ᴄʜᴇꜰ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴀᴜᴛʜᴏʀꜱ ɴᴏᴛᴇ:</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">i tried to reduce the tokens as much as I could</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">2420 &gt; 2041</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">should be better now 👍🏾</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 112px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/67311507-a983-44e8-89c4-a6959d459395_19a9bfec-0999-4e82-9b2e-e6d0fac982de.webp?width=1000\"></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"67311507-a983-44e8-89c4-a6959d459395_e8d82e0e-f7d4-48b5-981d-42070a3eadb6.jpg","creator":"EminemsSalsa","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","📚 Fictional","📺 Anime","🦸 Hero","⛓️ Dominant","👤 AnyPOV","⚔️ Enemies to Lovers"],"chats":15930,"messages":404018,"created_at":"2023-12-02T00:40:11.202825+00:00"}